    ADR-013 amendment posture (per CLAUDE.md §6.5):
      Endpoint continues to inject ONLY facade types
      (`IConsumerRoutingService` + `IInvokePlaybookAi`) from
      `Services/Ai/PublicContracts/`. New parameters (`IComposeDocumentService`,
